'''Tamssugurt n twwuri tanamunt''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|tsrɣint]] : تعاضدية العمل الاجتماعي)  tga yat tmssurt [[Lmɣrib|tamɣribit]],<ref>https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mutuelle_d%27action_sociale</ref> macc tga tar rrbḥ<ref>https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mutuelle_d%27action_sociale</ref>. Tasmiglt nns tamzwarut tga tt tiwisi n imltaɣn nns ig ttaḍnn nɣ ig mmutn. Ar asn tettaws s kraḍt tɣawsiwin<ref>https://ar.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A9_%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%85%D9%84_%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AC%D8%AA%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%8A</ref> : 
#iɣ ttaḍnn, ar tfrru tiɣṛaḍ n isafarn d tɣṛaḍ n ujujji.
#Ar tfrru iṛẓan n tmttant.
#Ar tfrru timqṛaḍ tikuyassin n umltaɣ abḍil.

== Amawal : ==
Amla ad gis tugt n tguriwin timaynutin, nẓḍar ad tnt naf g imawaln d isgzawaln n tmaziɣt, zun d ukan : 

* Tanamunt : taguri ad tga [[Afris]], iwckad sg wassaɣ n [[Amun]].
* Tamssugurt : taguri ad tga [[assaɣ]], s Tasrɣint : إدارة nɣ تعاضدية, tkkad taguri ad [[Amyag]] n Ssugr.
* Tamssurt : société
* Tasmiglt : tkkad [[Amyag]] n Siggl.
* Amltaɣ : منخرط

